<h1>Administration</h1>
<div>
    <p>This web application streamlines the management of short URLs, transforming lengthy web addresses into concise, shareable links.</p>
    <p>Key features include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Simple URL shortening: Convert long URLs into short, manageable links.</li>
        <li>User authentication: Secure access to the application with user roles.</li>
        <li>URL management: Create, update, and delete short URLs as needed.</li>
        <li>Scheduling: Set up one-time or recurring redirects for your short URLs.</li>
        <li>Performance tracking: Monitor click metrics to assess link engagement.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>By simplifying long URLs and providing scheduling and tracking capabilities, this tool enhances link sharing and management.</p>
</div>
